# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s22a_75c6f555:

    # "Oh god why? What have I done?"
    "Oh dios, ¿por qué? ¿Qué he hecho?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s22a_a109021c:

    # "Her back is turned to me like mine is to hers. I claw my nails deeper into the scratchy couch fabric and stick my gaze on the floor."
    "Ella me da la espalda, como yo a ella. Clavo mis uñas más profundo en la tela áspera del sofá y fijo la mirada en el suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s22a_2618cc38:

    # "Please end me now."
    "Por favor, acaben conmigo ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s22a_7854f2b9:

    # "It was silent after we did {i}that.{/i} Nice silence, a blissful release of silence. But as we walked back, terror started to sink in. I think she felt it, too."
    "Hubo silencio después de que hicimos {i}eso.{/i} Un silencio agradable, una liberación dichosa de silencio. Pero mientras caminábamos de regreso, el terror empezó a asentarse. Creo que ella también lo sintió."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s22a_4f24003f:

    # "I listen to the buzz of the generator, and stare at a patch of artifical light on the wall."
    "Escucho el zumbido del generador y me quedo mirando un parche de luz artificial en la pared."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s22a_3b382def:

    # "Stupid little box is making fun of me, I swear."
    "Esa estúpida cajita se está burlando de mí, lo juro."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s22a_d2ea78ed:

    # Marina "So what now?"
    Marina "Так что теперь?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s22a_4f384b76:

    # "Funny. That’s the same thing I asked when we found the treasure except she sounds even more hopeless and confused than I did."
    "Qué curioso. Eso mismo pregunté cuando encontramos el tesoro, solo que ella suena aún más desesperada y confundida de lo que yo estaba."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s22a_aac6effc:

    # "Bringing my legs to my chest, I bundle my arms around them and put on a nervous smirk."
    "Llevo mis piernas al pecho, las abrazo con los brazos y esbozo una sonrisa nerviosa."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s22a_65b1b2c7:

    # Amber "We could always go hiking again."
    Amber "Мы снова можем отправиться погулять."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s22a_7d12b10d:

    # "She throws a mock-slap at my shoulder, feigning a huffy voice."
    "Me da un manotazo fingido en el hombro, imitando una voz ofendida."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s22a_45e7dab0:

    # Marina "You {i}would{/i} like that, wouldn’t you?"
    Marina "Тебе бы этого {i}очень{/i} хотелось, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s22a_11545813:

    # "The heavy embarrassment in the air melts away into something a little more comfortable as we both manage to laugh at my perviness."
    "La pesada vergüenza en el aire se disipa en algo más cómodo mientras ambas logramos reírnos de mi perversidad."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s22a_cefa6635:

    # Marina "{cps=12}Waaaahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh.{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=12}Ааааааххх.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s22a_ea22d515:

    # "Marina lets out a whiny cry and slides against the couch."
    "Marina suelta un quejido lastimero y se desliza contra el sofá."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s22a_9d513e25:

    # Marina "{cps=80}But seriously, {w=0.4}what’re we going to {cps=15}doooooooooo?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=80}Но серьезно, {w=0.4}что мы будем {cps=15}дееелаааать?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s22a_6f839ac4:

    # Amber "About what?"
    Amber "С чем?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s22a_bc439461:

    # Marina "About everything!"
    Marina "Со всем!"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s22a_d7de5f65:

    # Marina "The treasure,{w=0.7} home..."
    Marina "Сокровищем,{w=0.7} домом..."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s22a_f164cb59:

    # Marina "Us…"
    Marina "Нами…"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s22a_2cea5fd1:

    # "My heart tightens like she’s squeezing it."
    "Mi corazón se aprieta como si ella lo estuviera exprimiendo."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s22a_a45e5e45:

    # Amber "Did you not…"
    Amber "Неужели тебе не было…"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s22a_f4c09bc6:

    # Marina "No! I did—"
    Marina "Нет—"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s22a_a5c2fbfc:

    # Marina "I do."
    Marina "Было."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s22a_13677b0c:

    # Marina "I just don’t know."
    Marina "Просто я не знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:138
translate spanish hwb_s22a_27eba5f0:

    # "She turns to me, her eyes pleading. Like she’s looking for answers."
    "Se vuelve hacia mí, con los ojos suplicantes. Como si buscara respuestas."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s22a_d58abd39:

    # "There's no doubt I'm responsible for those eyes."
    "No hay duda de que soy responsable de esos ojos."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s22a_0d4533ae:

    # "Feeling a fierce sense of responsibility, I shoot up and march to the center console."
    "Sintiendo un fuerte sentido de responsabilidad, me levanto de un salto y camino hacia la consola central."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s22a_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s22a_f897f573:

    # Amber "Hold on."
    Amber "Подожди."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s22a_417de252:

    # "I open the console, but don’t bother digging around. I know exactly where these are."
    "Abro la consola, pero no me molesto en revolver. Sé exactamente dónde están."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s22a_3d8a9ba4:

    # "Two irreplaceable pieces of paper."
    "Dos pedazos de papel irremplazables."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s22a_025b59a1:

    # "Stopping in front of the couch, my voice darkens."
    "Deteniéndome frente al sofá, mi voz se oscurece."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s22a_f68afd11:

    # Amber "I’ll be using my half of the treasure to pay for Gramps’ hospital and funeral expenses."
    Amber "Я использую свою часть сокровища, чтобы оплатить долг перед больницей и затраты на похороны дедушки."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s22a_0dcf6f82:

    # Amber "But before I do that, I still need to go to the music festival."
    Amber "Но прежде чем я это сделаю, мне все еще нужно добраться до музыкального фестиваля."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s22a_a7e199ef:

    # "I offer her one of the tickets. Unsure, she gently tugs it from my hand and begins reading."
    "Le ofrezco uno de los boletos. Dudando, lo toma suavemente de mi mano y comienza a leer."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s22a_8ea8d46f:

    # Amber "If you want to, you can go with me. Might give you a little extra time to think about things."
    Amber "Если ты хочешь, мы можем пойти вместе. Может быть это даст нам время на раздумья."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s22a_2c1d24fe:

    # "My voice softens."
    "Mi voz se suaviza."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:186
translate spanish hwb_s22a_0b661ef3:

    # Amber "About everything."
    Amber "Обо всем."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s22a_48b8ff87:

    # Marina "Th-{w=0.2}The festival? Me?"
    Marina "На-{w=0.2}на фестиваль? Я?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s22a_cf519e4c:

    # Amber "Up to you, babe."
    Amber "Решать тебе, детка."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s22a_9b040eb9:

    # "I flop back on the couch and hold the ticket over my eyes to block out the light."
    "Me dejo caer de espaldas en el sofá y sostengo el boleto sobre mis ojos para bloquear la luz."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s22a_0e7fe9d3:

    # Marina "{cps=10}Ohhhhhhhhhh?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=10}Оооооу?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s22a_6a0ed89c:

    # "Oh crap."
    "Oh, rayos."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s22a_034400d6:

    # "She peels the ticket off halfway and peeks through, revealing an amused grin."
    "Ella levanta el boleto a medias y se asoma por debajo, revelando una sonrisa divertida."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s22a_9da87e51:

    # Marina "So I’m ‘babe’ now, huh?"
    Marina "Теперь я “детка”, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s22a_a54b71ee:

    # "On her hands and knees, Marina crawls ever so closer, while I scramble to turn and hide my face."
    "En manos y rodillas, Marina se arrastra cada vez más cerca, mientras yo me revuelvo para girarme y esconder mi cara."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s22a_f773fcf0:

    # Amber "Shut up. It was an accident."
    Amber "Замолчи. Это была случайность."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s22a_32efd8b0:

    # "And now I’m back to where I started: mortified and embarrassed."
    "Y ahora estoy de vuelta donde empecé: aterrada y avergonzada."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s22a_a13e128c:

    # Marina "Amber."
    Marina "Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s22a_e4dff008:

    # "Her voice is like a melody."
    "Su voz es como una melodía."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s22a_f7d07288:

    # Amber "Shut up."
    Amber "Замолчи."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s22a_1c3e268c:

    # Marina "{cps=15}Aaaamber.{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=15}Эээээмбер.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s22a_bfac190c:

    # Amber "I said shut up."
    Amber "Да замолчишь ты или нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s22a_401d90d7:

    # Marina "Oh Amber."
    Marina "О, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s22a_5f1d9671:

    # Amber "What?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s22a_1395d4c6:

    # "A tank engine plows into my back, followed by soft, gentle arms wrapping around my neck as she rests her head against mine."
    "Un motor de tanque se estrella contra mi espalda, seguido de brazos suaves y tiernos que se envuelven alrededor de mi cuello mientras apoya su cabeza contra la mía."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s22a_6189d3c2:

    # Marina "Thank you."
    Marina "Спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s22a_1543f5d5:

    # "My shoulders relax, embracing her. In turn, I rest my head on hers, too. A head sandwich."
    "Mis hombros se relajan, abrazándola. A mi vez, apoyo mi cabeza sobre la suya también. Un sándwich de cabezas."

# game/script/hwb_s22a.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s22a_aa60a0de:

    # Amber "Sure thing, kiddo."
    Amber "Всегда пожалуйста, малышка."

